Legal Checkmate

	Philosophy

		-
			A state of legal checkmate is created when an individual or group is in a situation
			where they are not in violation of the law, but where it is effectively impossible for
			them to proceed without being in violation of the law.
		-

	Principles

		Legal Absurdity

			-
				The aspects of the law that are capable of generating states of legal checkmate are
				referred to as conditions of legal absurdity.
			-